Package ui.drawing.composition

Interface SectionComposer<T extends Section>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of sections that can be stored in the composer.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Section
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    OrderedSectionComposer<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BasicSectionComposer, BufferedSectionComposer, LabeledMenuItem, NoOverlapSectionComposer
    public interface SectionComposer<T extends Section>
extends Section
    Represents a collections of sections with positions that can be specified that are drawn together.
